   gABRIEL SAT DOWN. HIS EYES FULL OF DETERMINATION. HE PULLED OUT A DEVISE. 
IT SHOWED A STATUE OF KIT KAT. THE MEMORIAL TO HER IN THE CAPTITAL CITY. HE 
FACE WAS NOT ON IT FOR THERE WHERE NO DATATRACKS IN THE FUTURE OF WHAT SHE 
LOOKED LIKE. INSCRIBED AT THE BOTTOM OF THE HOLOGRAM WAS THE PHRASE.."LET OUR 
PATHS LEAD WHERE THEY MAY." kIT kAT.PAST EARTH. DAY OF DESTRUCTION.
    THAT IS WHAT THEY NAMED THE DAY OF THE FALL OF THE ALLIANCE. HE HOPED SHE 
WOULD UNDERSTAND. "MY LEGEND YOU ARE MORE IMPORTANT THEN YOU KNOW. YOU LEAD 
THE FIGHT AGAINST THE ALLAINCE. YOU SAVE THE PREDACON EMPIRE. IT IS ALSO THE 
DAY THE THE GREAT MEGATRON WAS DESTROYED. BY YOUR HAND. THIER ARE TALES OF 
YOU AND DESTRUCTOR. HOW YOU JOURNEYED THROUGH THE UNIVERSE MAKEING A TOTAL 
PREDACON RULE. BUT SOMEONE IS DESTROYING MY WORLD.  SOMEONE HAS TAMPERED WITH 
THE TIME STREAM. THE ALLAINCE IS WINNING. IF YOU WANT THIS FUTURE..YOU MUSY 
FUFILL YOUR DESTINY. DESTROY THE ALLIANCE OR ALL IS LOST"
